Package hapi.services.rudder Description

Provides generated classes and interfaces for writing rudders—Tiller plugins—from Java.

Documentation of the classes and interfaces in this package is authored by the Kubernetes Helm team.

Author:
The Kubernetes Helm team
See Also:
Issue #1924 (the Rudder proposal)
